{
  "texts": [
    "Once a woman Veteran opted-in for DPP enrollment, they were provided a unique voucher code that they could use to register and enroll with the virtual DPP vendor which was delivered by a CDC-recognized, third-party DPP organization.",
    "The virtual DPP vendor tracked participation and weight change data which was provided back to local VA sites to track participant progress.",
    "MeasuresOur main outcome of interest was enrollment in DPP, defined as redeeming the unique voucher and completing enrollment in the virtual DPP platform.",
    "Our regressor of interest was a dichotomous indicator of prior use of VA preventative services for weight management or T2D prevention (1 = yes for any versus 0 = none).",
    "Use of any of the following within the last three years was included in our composite outcome of interest: (1) MOVE!"
  ]
}